---
// Redirect /review to the FAS Motorsports Google Business Profile review page.
// Used on printed materials, QR codes, and email campaigns.
//
// TO FILL IN: Replace PLACE_ID_HERE with the actual Google Place ID.
// How to find it:
//   1. Go to https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/places/web-service/place-id
//      and use the Place ID Finder with "FAS Motorsports, 6161 Riverside Dr, Punta Gorda, FL 33982"
//   2. Or search Google Maps for FAS Motorsports, click Share → Copy link,
//      and extract the ID from the URL (the string after "1s" in the /maps/place/... path)
//
// Final URL format: https://search.google.com/local/writereview?placeid=PLACE_ID_HERE
return Astro.redirect('https://search.google.com/local/writereview?placeid=PLACE_ID_HERE', 302);
---
